<p><i><b>Simulacra and Simulation</b></i> (<i><b>Simulacres et Simulation</b></i> in <a href="/wiki/French_language" title="French language">French</a>) is a <a href="/wiki/Philosophy" title="Philosophy">philosophical</a> <a href="/wiki/Treatise" title="Treatise">treatise</a> by <a href="/wiki/Jean_Baudrillard" title="Jean Baudrillard">Jean Baudrillard</a> that discusses the interaction between reality, symbols and society.</p>
